data-triple-N3.o: "The Royal Academy of Arts (RA, traditionally written as R.A. ) is an art institution based in Burlington House on Piccadilly in London, United Kingdom. It has a unique position in being an independent, privately funded institution led by eminent artists and architects whose purpose is to promote the creation, enjoyment and appreciation of the visual arts through exhibitions, education and debate."@en
